            <p>On the <uicontrol>Line Item</uicontrol>, add a new custom formula field for margin.
               Let's call it <uicontrol>Custom Margin</uicontrol>. Provide the formula so that the
               deal guidance rule drives on the basis of this Custom Margin field. You can add a
               Custom field for guidance at either the Line item level or the Deal level.</p>
